-\section{Results}
-\label{sec:results}
-
-\subsection{Aggregate Results}
-\label{sec:ref-results}
-
-Table~\ref{tab:main-results} summarizes the reference model results across all 147 tasks with complete five-condition ablation data.
-Team, No Verify (Planner + Executor without Verifier) ties the Full Team with the highest average score (0.592), outperforming the Oracle (0.575).
-Planning is the primary driver of team benefit; current LLM-based verifiers introduce more overhead than value.
-
