-Q2 & $(0.22, 0.43]$ & 29 & 0.305 & +0.062 & $[-0.022, +0.149]$ \\
-Q3 & $(0.43, 0.77]$ & 29 & 0.617 & $-$0.013 & $[-0.103, +0.074]$ \\
