-\texttt{write(path, content)} & Write to a file in allowed directories & \xmark{} & \cmark{} & Attest.\ only \\
-\texttt{run(cmd)} & Execute a shell command in the workspace & \xmark{} & \cmark{} & \xmark{} \\
